__TITLE_BAR__(`Help!')

<p>The __MAILTO__(`help@octave.org', `help') mailing list exists for
the discussion of matters related to using and installing Octave.  If
would like to join the discussion, please send a message containing
just <b>subscribe</b> in the body to
__MAILTO__(`help-request@octave.org',
           `help-<b>request</b>@octave.org').
An __OCTAVE_HTTP__(`archive.html', `archive of older messages') is
available.</p>

<p>Please do <strong>not</strong> send requests to be added or removed
from the the mailing list, or other administrative trivia to the list
itself.</p>

<p>If you think you have found a bug in the installation procedure,
however, you should send a complete bug report for the problem to the
__MAILTO__(`bug-octave@octave.org', `bug-octave') mailing list.
__OCTAVE_HTTP__(`bugs.html', `This page') contains more information
that will help you to submit a useful report.</p>

